ish-terror-is-jeopardizing-israels-existence/00000191-7b9a-de04-af9b-7b9b38070000</link><description>罗南·巴尔在一封信中警告说，“犹太恐怖分子领导人想让系统失去控制，这对以色列造成的损害是难以形容的”。他说，警察的无能和公共合法性导致了犹太恐怖主义的扩张</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 20:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-chief-warns-pm-and-ministers-jewish-terror-is-jeopardizing-israels-existence/00000191-7b9a-de04-af9b-7b9b38070000</guid></item><item><title>“政治性大于人道主义”：加沙援助运动使巴勒斯坦以色列人分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/more-political-than-humanitarian-aid-campaigns-for-gaza-divide-palestinian-israelis/00000191-7082-d988-a3b5-71ea1de40000</link><description>救援工作正在动员以色列各地的人们捐赠、分类和包装食品和必需品，但一些巴勒斯坦以色列人表示，他们正在考虑参与犹太-阿拉伯联合行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 19:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/more-political-than-humanitarian-aid-campaigns-for-gaza-divide-palestinian-israelis/00000191-7082-d988-a3b5-71ea1de40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医生规避法律，向父母收取巨额费用来选择婴儿的性别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bypassing-the-law-israeli-doctors-charge-parents-a-fortune-to-select-their-babys-sex/00000191-7b16-daab-a3f3-fb96bb6d0000</link><description>在以色列，性别选择是非法的。 《国土报》的一项调查显示，在国外，医生整个行业的基础就是这样做。有些家长愿意付给他们巨额费用</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 18:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bypassing-the-law-israeli-doctors-charge-parents-a-fortune-to-select-their-babys-sex/00000191-7b16-daab-a3f3-fb96bb6d0000</guid></item><item><title>“这正在杀害犹太人民，使我们分裂。”内塔尼亚胡怎么会看不到这一点呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-hostage-omer-neutra-praise-biden-slam-netanyahu-at-dnc/00000191-7afe-dfa2-a5b9-fbff7a2f0000